headline: Fiserv to Acquire AIB Merchant Services
summary: MILWAUKEE & DUBLIN, June 06, 2025--Fiserv, Inc. (NYSE: FI), a leading global provider of payments and financial services technology, announced today that it has agreed to acquire the remaining 49.9% of AIB Merchant Services (AIBMS), its joint venture with AIB Group, in a transaction focused on driving continued growth in Ireland and the broader European market.
